description: Forest Department - Order to declare - the Magurugoda Forest in Karavita, Elapata D/S Division, Ratnapura District and Galaha Forest (part) in Stalen Burg Estate, Udapalatha D/S Division, Kandy District as Conservation Forests - Kurakkanhena Kanda Forest in Kurakkanhenegedara, Kalupota D/S Division, Kurunegala District and Wellangolla Forest in Ihala Eruwula and Wewala Wewa, Dambulla D/S Division, Matale District as Reserved Forest from 07.04.2014
